Creating a test file:

For any illumina paired read set:
first.fq, second.fq

bash:
split -n 6 first.fq
sed -i 's/^[^@+]/TAA/g' xaa
sed -i 's/^[^@+]/TGTAA/g' xab
sed -i 's/^[^@+]/ATCTAA/g' xac
sed -i 's/^[^@+]/GTTCCTAA/g' xad
sed -i 's/^[^@+]/CCGCGGTAA/g' xae
#leave xaf to have no cut site

cat x* > first.mod.fq
